name: jellyfish vibin'
description:
Explore the sea as a goldfish on a mission! Collect jellyfish and return to Professor Octopus for his unique appraisal. You'll get to know the specimen you collect one by one. Interact with quirky NPCs, and discover a side quest along the way for the ultimate prize a fish could ever dream of. Enjoy funky music and a retro, dithered low-poly world. 

Includes dynamic materials that randomly colorize the jellyfish in your level for a unique, replayable visual experience!

This prototype was developed in two weeks as my personal project for Code Coven's IGM with Unreal Engine 2022.
